{
  "stem": "13471.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "After Duke, I got a job teaching at Washington and Lee.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Washington and Lee is in Lexington, Virginia.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Named Washington and Lee because when George Washington left the army of the United States and became president, the state of Virginia gave him a monetary reward.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was something like $15,000, I've forgotten now what it was.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was a number of shares in a certain canal company.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Anyway.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he refused to accept them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And instead he knew of this little struggling school up in the Shenandoah Valley called Liberty Academy or something.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he gave it to them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they renamed themselves Washington College in honor of this gift.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "By the way, it's still there, and I have profited by income from it.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But anyway.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And then when-- when the Civil War was over, the question of what we're going to do with Robert E Lee.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And the same little college offered him a position as president.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And he accepted.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And then after his death, they changed it to Washington and Lee University.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "It's-- it's a fine private university.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was '37 to '41.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I taught German, well-- and I also taught French and English.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Will you believe it?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Triple threat man.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Mhm.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] I, I put in, in the spring of 1941, for a fellowship to go to Wisconsin, study at Wisconsin.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "All right.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There were two types of fellowship at Wisconsin at that point.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was the $400 number, and a $600 number.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] That may not sound like much today.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But for, for you-- a single man, as a student, if you wanted to do a couple of jobs like waiting on tables, could get by, you see, for an academic year on $600.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So anyway, I was real tickled.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I got a 600-bucker.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
